window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Myrddin is overjoyed to have been joined by a son he never knew he had, but he struggles to come to terms with his dreams and faces treachery on every side in his quest to save King Arthur from the fate that awaits him. </p> <p>Nell, in turn, must choose between the life she left behind and the life before her, even if neither can last for even one more day.<i> Of Men and Dragons</i> is the riveting third act in the Lion of Wales series. </p> <p>Complete series listening order: <i>Cold My Heart, The Oaken Door, Of Men and Dragons, A Long Cloud, Frost Against the Hilt.</i></p>"; 
